text: Love Myself is an electropop song and debut single by actress and singer Hailee Steinfeld, released on August 7, 2015. It is from her debut EP, Haiz. The lyrics speak of self-confidence, and an "ode to masturbation" in the media. It reached the top 10 in Belgium, Israel,https://archive.today/20151104171131/http://www.mediaforest.biz/WeeklyCharts/HistoryWeeklyCharts.aspx?year=2015&week;=44 and the United States. ==References== Category:Electropop Category:Pop songs Category:2015 songs
